FSA Datasets by Topic

Source: vignettes/FSA_byTopic.Rmd
FSA_byTopic.Rmd

The following datasets found in the FSA and FSAdata packages are arranged by major fisheries topic. This list was last updated on November 24, 2022.

 

Length Expansion

Dataset Description
FSAdata::BluntnoseIL1 Subampled lengths of Bluntnose Minnows from Inch Lake, WI.
FSAdata::TroutperchLM3 Subsampled lengths of Troutperch from Lake Michigan, 1977.

 

Length Conversion

Dataset Description
FSAdata::BluegillLM Lengths and weights for Bluegill from Lake Mary, MN.
FSAdata::LakeTroutALTER Biological data for Lake Trout from the Arctic LTER (AK).
FSAdata::Pallid Lengths and weights for Pallid Sturgeon from four locations in the Missouri River.

FSAdata::Morwong2 Ages of Morwong assigned from otoliths by Reader B at two times.
FSAdata::Morwong3 Ages of Morwong assigned from otoliths by two readers.
FSAdata::MulletBS Ages of Red Mullet assigned from whole and broken-burnt otoliths.
FSAdata::MuskieSLR Ages of Muskellunge assigned from scales and cleithra.
FSAdata::PygmyWFBC Biological data for Pygmy Whitefish from Dina Lake #1 (British Columbia), 2000 and 2001.
FSAdata::ShadCR Ages of American Shad assigned from scales by three readers at two times.
FSAdata::StripedBass1 Ages of Striped Bass assigned from scales and otoliths.
FSAdata::StripedBass4 Ages of Striped Bass assigned from scales by two readers.
FSAdata::StripedBass5 Ages of Striped Bass assigned from otoliths by two readers.
FSAdata::StripedBass6 Ages of Striped Bass assigned from scales and otoliths.
FSAdata::WalleyePS Ages of Walleye assigned from otoliths, scales, and spines.
FSAdata::WhitefishMB Ages of Lake Whitefish from four lakes assigned from scales and fin-rays.
FSAdata::YTFlounder Ages of Yellowtail Flounder assigned from scales and otoliths.

FSAdata::SalmonADP Catches in removal events of salmon parr.
FSAdata::SalmonidsMCCA Catches in removal events of Cutthroate Trout and Steelhead of various sizes in two reaches of McGarvey Creek (CA).
FSAdata::SimonsonLyons Catches in removal events of trout at various locations.
FSAdata::TroutADP Catches in removal events of trout.
